    Introduce more reliable package prediction for slackware stock
     packages and SlackBuild.org compiled ones. Minor bugfixes.

0.2.4 (2009-10-15):
    Introduced options for help and version, and to enable/disable logfile
     and package prediction.
    Executable pyfind_revdep has changed its name in pyfindrevdep to avoid
     confusion with the main module (if you are upgrading from a previous
     version, you would want to erase "pyfind_revdep" file.

0.2.3 (2009-10-07):
    First public release (with experimental package prediction)

0.1.0 (2009-09-30):
    First internal release.

